                     <interp inst="t17791208-12-off63" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17791208-12-off63" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a copper tea-kettle, value 5 s. a pair of bellows, value 2 s. and a flat iron, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17791208-12-victim142" type="victimName">
                     James
                      Bowker
                  <interp inst="t17791208-12-victim142" type="surname" value="Bowker"></interp>
