               <p>I am a constable. I saw the things all found upon the prisoner. I was in the house when the prisoner came in, and 1when she went out.</p>
               <p>(The things were produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I only beg the mercy of the court. I have nothing more to say.</p>
